text: Hui Chen Chen (born 23 April 1988) is a Taiwanese volleyball player. She played for the Chinese Taipei women's national volleyball team. She played at the 2006 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship and 2006 Asian Games. She played for National Kaohsiung Normal University's women's volleyball team. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese volleyball players
